query:
/*+  */ select count(*)
from question AS q
inner join tag_question AS tq
on tq.question_id = q.id AND q.view_count >= 100 AND q.view_count <= 100000
inner join site AS s
on tq.site_id = s.site_id AND q.site_id = s.site_id AND s.site_name IN ('stackoverflow')
inner join tag AS t
on tq.tag_id = t.id AND t.site_id = s.site_id AND t.name IN ('blackberry-10',
'derby',
'glfw',
'google-analytics-api',
'graph-theory',
'implicit-conversion',
'masm',
'mediawiki',
'oozie',
'python-asyncio',
'python-unittest',
'qmake',
'raphael',
'tableau');
